<abstract>New York City Lead Service Line Locations, 2026 is a polygon theme representing tax lots with information regarding the presence of lead in their water service lines as of 2026. Columbia library staff accessed this data in April of 2026 from the NYC Open Data portal at https://data.cityofnewyork.us/Environment/Lead-Service-Line-Location-Coordinates/jqfp-uff7/about_data and has provided it in the geopackage format. A codebook is included in the full download package.
